d the bacteria in reverse order. This incorrectly implied that <italic>entomophila</italic> was cultured at 37 degrees for 16h and <italic>aeruginosa</italic> at 30 degrees for 10h. The authors apologize for any inconvenience caused by this mistake.</p><p>The article has been corrected accordingly.</p></body></article>